{"tid":1579354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我作為連登首席美斯迷，響應大和解，宣佈暫時不反C朗了，以後球壇就係絕代雙嬌。","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T09:02:39.000Z","uid":43785,"like":70,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"de1c965e87b4a2de3a9fa017d31a663f55cb2be1","tid":1579354,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"我作為連登首席美斯迷，同小巴塞迷<br />\n睇左張相好感動。<br />\n<br />\n現在我決定響應足球球迷大和解，宣布暫時不反C朗了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jtTLRkV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjtTLRkV.jpg&h=62a8ae6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n球壇有兩個球王稱霸左足球場十幾年。<br />\n除左對方，就再冇人可以同佢相提並論。<br />\n我想呼籲波台手足，以後就只有絕代雙嬌，雙球王，大家點睇？<br />\n我相信我地作為美斯球迷，先放下身段，唔攻擊朗迷，應該可以少左好多紛爭。<br />\n<br />\n美斯既比賽同C朗既比賽，都係睇得一場得一場。<br />\n大家應該好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再比黎比去了。<br />\n<br />\n美斯受左傷，睇唔到佢扭波既英姿，個心好傷心，心諗都唔知仲有幾多場可以睇到。<br />\n美斯退休，除左C朗，我都唔知可以再睇邊個踢波了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能，若有一天，我們失去兩位球王，我都唔會懂得再喜歡足球了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c9dba4815ecad4889160fce99e7d1687af17eb","tid":1579354,"uid":34444,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"7d8d27fddc18004310ee4bb2bbe8f1467a49c314","tid":1579354,"uid":14126,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"Sir!!!!"},{"pid":"4991d3e384c269c94a233d57244713519789ded5","tid":1579354,"uid":43231,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"30bfaf22a297beb12fc45df9591500468b468533","tid":1579354,"uid":25520,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"cc238301f1ff8f58bd167d0d87e75c05303d25e6","tid":1579354,"uid":42192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"Good